<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>系统公告 - SSL Online Judge</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header.high {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dc3545;
        }
        .header.normal {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffc107;
        }
        .header.low {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .logo.high {
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .logo.normal {
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        .logo.low {
            color: #007bff;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .title.high {
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .title.normal {
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        .title.low {
            color: #007bff;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .announcement-box {
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .announcement-box.high {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
        }
        .announcement-box.normal {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
        }
        .announcement-box.low {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
        }
        .priority-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .priority-badge.high {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
        }
        .priority-badge.normal {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: #212529;
        }
        .priority-badge.low {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
        }
        .announcement-content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #6c757d;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }
        .announcement-content.high {
            border-left-color: #dc3545;
        }
        .announcement-content.normal {
            border-left-color: #ffc107;
        }
        .announcement-content.low {
            border-left-color: #007bff;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .action-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 10px 5px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header {{priority}}">
            <div class="logo {{priority}}">SSL Online Judge</div>
            <div>系统公告通知</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="announcement-box {{priority}}">
            <div class="priority-badge {{priority}}">
                {{#if (eq priority "high")}}
                    🚨 紧急公告
                {{else if (eq priority "normal")}}
                    📢 重要公告
                {{else}}
                    📝 一般公告
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="icon">
                {{#if (eq priority "high")}}
                    🚨
                {{else if (eq priority "normal")}}
                    📢
                {{else}}
                    📝
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="title {{priority}}">{{title}}</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="announcement-content {{priority}}">
                <h4>📋 公告内容：</h4>
                <div style="margin: 15px 0; line-height: 1.8;">
                    {{{content}}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if (eq priority "high")}}
                <div style="background-color: #f8d7da; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; color: #721c24;">
                    <h4>⚠️ 紧急提醒：</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>此为紧急公告，请立即关注</li>
                        <li>可能影响系统正常使用</li>
                        <li>请按照公告要求及时处理</li>
                        <li>如有疑问请立即联系管理员</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            {{else if (eq priority "normal")}}
                <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; color: #856404;">
                    <h4>📌 重要提醒：</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>此为重要公告，请仔细阅读</li>
                        <li>可能涉及系统功能变更</li>
                        <li>建议收藏此邮件以备查看</li>
                        <li>如有问题请联系技术支持</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            {{else}}
                <div style="background-color: #d1ecf1; border: 1px solid #bee5eb; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; color: #0c5460;">
                    <h4>💡 温馨提示：</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>此为一般性公告信息</li>
                        <li>建议了解相关内容</li>
                        <li>有助于更好地使用平台</li>
                        <li>欢迎提出意见和建议</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="action-box">
                <h4>🔗 相关操作：</h4>
                <a href="{{websiteUrl}}" class="btn">访问平台</a>
                <a href="{{websiteUrl}}/announcements" class="btn">查看所有公告</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #6c757d; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4>📞 联系我们：</h4>
                <p>如果您对此公告有任何疑问或需要帮助，请通过以下方式联系我们：</p>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li><strong>技术支持：</strong> support@ssloj.com</li>
                    <li><strong>管理员：</strong> admin@ssloj.com</li>
                    <li><strong>官方网站：</strong> <a href="{{websiteUrl}}">{{websiteUrl}}</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>此邮件由SSL Online Judge系统自动发送，请勿回复。</p>
            <p>我们会定期发送重要公告，请关注您的邮箱。</p>
            <p>感谢您使用SSL Online Judge平台！</p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 SSL Online Judge. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>